HEADWORD: Totalize
<hw>To"tal*ize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To make total,
or complete; to reduce to completeness.</def>
<rj><au>Coleridge.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Totalize</ent>⟦br⟧

